headline.print_headline: Chinese Online Cosmetics Retailer Jumei Files for $400 Million U.S. IPO
headline.main: Chinese Online Cosmetics Retailer Jumei Files for $400 Million U.S. IPO

lead_paragraph: Jumei International Holding Ltd, backed by venture-capital firm Sequoia Capital, filed with U.S. regulators on Friday to raise up to $400 million in an initial public offering of American Depositary Shares.
